hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: What company are you calling from? aspen pharmacare us Detroit, shifty cops, double-crosses, ambitious criminals. The duo of Strong and James is crazy good. From the opening seconds of the premiere, the two actors establish a riveting dynamic using little more than facial expressions and line delivery. On that note, this is a show that respects its audience enough to toss viewers into a situation with minimal information and expect them to engage with the story. This is a murder mystery from the point of view of sympathetic killers; the tightrope walk of staying one step ahead of an ever-changing game certainly works in the pilot, and the storytellers appear confident enough to continue along this course.
